797
01:04:18,159 --> 01:04:20,489
I know you've been understanding.

798
01:04:21,429 --> 01:04:22,429
I appreciate it.

799
01:04:23,429 --> 01:04:25,929
The company is back on track now.

800
01:04:28,039 --> 01:04:29,340
Am I still...

801
01:04:30,239 --> 01:04:31,840
your second priority?

802
01:04:32,769 --> 01:04:34,840
- It's not like that.
- It is.

803
01:04:36,510 --> 01:04:39,309
Didn't you see me
get hit by the ball earlier?

804
01:04:39,349 --> 01:04:43,420
Did you expect me to
run to you and comfort you...

805
01:04:43,989 --> 01:04:45,820
in front of all the employees?

806
01:04:45,849 --> 01:04:50,119
What about Mr. Kang?
He even kissed Yi Soo.

807
01:04:50,659 --> 01:04:51,730
That's...

808
01:04:52,260 --> 01:04:56,000
Treat me at least fairly.
I'm one of your employees.

809
01:04:56,099 --> 01:04:58,329
How could you not
write to me?

810
01:05:01,539 --> 01:05:02,570
The thing is...

811
01:05:05,940 --> 01:05:07,309
I did write one to you.

812
01:05:08,809 --> 01:05:12,179
I put more effort into yours
than any others'.

813
01:05:13,710 --> 01:05:17,019
I rewrote it countless times.

814
01:05:19,019 --> 01:05:22,420
I wanted to convey my feelings...

815
01:05:22,989 --> 01:05:26,159
just the way they are.

816
01:05:28,599 --> 01:05:30,429
That's just an excuse.

817
01:05:30,969 --> 01:05:32,099
Forget it.

818
01:05:32,900 --> 01:05:35,900
You just don't love me.

819
01:05:35,940 --> 01:05:38,840
- Why do you say that?
- To me, love is not...

820
01:05:39,010 --> 01:05:41,480
hesitating or thinking what to do.

821
01:05:41,579 --> 01:05:43,579
It's not something you do
with your head.

822
01:05:43,679 --> 01:05:45,849
You have to dive into it
like a crazy person.

823
01:05:46,179 --> 01:05:48,320
I'm not that kind of person.

824
01:05:51,150 --> 01:05:52,420
Of course not.

825
01:05:55,119 --> 01:05:56,389
You'll get wet.

826
01:05:57,960 --> 01:06:00,059
I'm this kind of person.

827
01:06:16,139 --> 01:06:19,309
- Oh, my. Ro Woon, you're soaked.
- Ro Woon.

828
01:06:19,349 --> 01:06:21,119
You'll catch a cold.

829
01:06:21,579 --> 01:06:23,380
- Why did you walk in the rain?
- You're soaked.

830
01:06:23,420 --> 01:06:25,090
- What is this?
- Why did you do that?

831
01:06:25,119 --> 01:06:26,889
- Oh, my.
- You shouldn't do this.

832
01:06:28,219 --> 01:06:29,889
What is this sound?

833
01:06:30,489 --> 01:06:32,289
Oh, my. Look at that.

834
01:06:32,360 --> 01:06:34,030
- Oh, my.
- Gosh.

835
01:06:35,059 --> 01:06:37,599
- What's going on?
- It's unbelievable.

836
01:06:50,179 --> 01:06:51,179
Oh, my.

837
01:07:06,360 --> 01:07:09,030
Ro Woon, I love you.

838
01:07:09,530 --> 01:07:10,829
I love you.

839
01:07:11,530 --> 01:07:12,900
I love you, Ro Woon!

840
01:07:17,170 --> 01:07:18,269
Go.

841
01:07:19,409 --> 01:07:20,840
I love you, Chae Ro Woon!

842
01:07:22,409 --> 01:07:23,639
I love you!

843
01:07:51,309 --> 01:07:52,969
Where did you get hit by the ball?

844
01:07:53,139 --> 01:07:54,679
- Pardon?
- Is it here?

845
01:07:56,780 --> 01:07:58,110
Everyone's watching.

846
01:07:58,949 --> 01:08:00,050
Wait, is it here?

847
01:08:01,920 --> 01:08:03,250
It must be here.

848
01:08:05,690 --> 01:08:07,789
My goodness.

849
01:08:08,219 --> 01:08:09,320
I love you.

850
01:08:15,360 --> 01:08:17,869
- My goodness.
- Gosh.

851
01:08:21,670 --> 01:08:22,800
I can't watch.

852
01:08:30,640 --> 01:08:32,180
That's enough now.

853
01:08:34,109 --> 01:08:36,149
Get a room, you two.

854
01:08:44,930 --> 01:08:47,159
(Thank you for watching
My Shy Boss.)

855
01:09:13,020 --> 01:09:15,819
(My Shy Boss)

856
01:09:16,319 --> 01:09:18,430
- My Shy Boss, let's go.
